dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:41:31.000Z","msg":"薩德導彈就係奧巴馬搞出黎ge，好明顯係韓國總統ge問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727ec18c31cc2530dae230156ed0d62571a89345","tid":2394424,"uid":244797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"57623ca07c4ebfd26e49f83c7b4d986ae0ef22b7","tid":2394424,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0be78ef78b0c4e5badd579790f7fda4f3460f074","tid":2394424,"uid":244797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:40:38.000Z","msg":"又一個國家行動表態<br />\n唔係連登仔針對拜登 係所有國家都唔信拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:41:31.000Z","msg":"薩德導彈就係奧巴馬搞出黎ge，好明顯係韓國總統ge問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:44:48.000Z","msg":"咁我話泡菜仔都唔信佢有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da957d52ed3c2f45a19b375e0e4f9e6af817b297","tid":2394424,"uid":219244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:45:43.000Z","msg":"屌 例返轉咪一樣<br />\n日本到一樣好憎南韓，不過兩個焗住係美國大佬嘅關照下扮friend，而家扯爛塊面唔扮fd啦，不過益咗中國嚕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前日本有個民意調查<br />\n<br />\n日本人最憎南韓<br />\n其次北韓<br />\n第三先係中國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東北亞真係俾啲垃圾民族主義玩死<br />\n美國都禁唔住南韓啲濕鳩民族主義<br />\n南韓揼咗好多錢落去搞海軍，但係假想敵反而唔係北韓反而係日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喂，日本依家和平憲法嘅情況之下點會可能侵略南韓呀，擺明係民族主義作祟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f657d91c6a50f8ee5b29d31ae3be37e9572518","tid":2394424,"uid":246119,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"57623ca07c4ebfd26e49f83c7b4d986ae0ef22b7","tid":2394424,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0be78ef78b0c4e5badd579790f7fda4f3460f074","tid":2394424,"uid":244797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:40:38.000Z","msg":"又一個國家行動表態<br />\n唔係連登仔針對拜登 係所有國家都唔信拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:41:31.000Z","msg":"薩德導彈就係奧巴馬搞出黎ge，好明顯係韓國總統ge問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"韓國總統文在寅父母是脫北者。希望在兩韓和平統一後，能夠帶母親到朝鮮探訪故鄉。"}]}